channel.title: Object spawning walls fails?
channel.description:
When I try to spawn any type of wall object it doesn't show up. Any other type of object works fine like barrels and bank booths. But when I go into a map editor and look at pre-spawned objects like pest control walls, I take the code and try to spawn the walls like this
[code] makeGlobalObject(2541, 3562, 14210, -1, 10); makeGlobalObject(2540, 3562, 14210, -1, 10);[/code]
nothing evens shows up, all advice/help is appreciated.
Thanks, Moose
